text: Prosopocera angolensis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Quedenfeldt in 1885. It has a wide distribution throughout Africa.BioLib.cz - Prosopocera angolensis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Prosopocerini Category:Beetles described in 1885
